creator: Zahra University (Online)
descriptionHtml:
There is following Rohani Ilaj you can read
Aurad-o-wazaif parhne ka tariqa

1- Ankhon k emraz k liye mujrab wazifa
2- Nazr kamzor ho jaye ya chali jaye tu konsa wazifa kre
3- Ankhoon k safaid aur kale motiye ka elaj
4- Emaan per khatma hoga inshallah
5- Sahib-e-aulad ho jaye ge ap wazifa ko ba kasrat se krey
6- Banjh pan ka elaaj ka mujraab amal
7- Neik aulad ki wiladat hoga
8- Jald he betey k maa bap ban jaye ge
9- Barj bari ho rahi ho tu usko rokne k liye
10- Har qism k bukhar k liye jo dawa se na jata ho
11- Mirgi ka bukhar nazla khansi har qisam ke dard aur emraz chashm k liye
12- Bukhar wale k monh per cheente mare jata rahe ga
13- Pathri k sabab ya garam cheezon k sabab se pishab men khoon ane lagta ho
14- Peit k dard men ifaqa hoga
15- Jigar ya meday k emraz k liye
descriptionShort: Ab Har Bemari Ka Ilaj Rohni Tareqe Se Kare Poore Imaan Aur Yaqeen K Sath
